<br>
 Is it possible to bootstrap from very low levels of language?<br>
<br>
 I can easily teach my human companion my native barbarian, for example, perhaps 10 seconds of conversation<br>
 before she has learned a point.  However we have been trying to bootstrap each other on Erudite. She knows only a point or two, And was sucessful in teaching me 2 points. since  then we have not been able to generate a message saying that either of us has learned another point.<br>
<br>
